tweet: Get Active! Physical activity is very important for people with diabetes! The goal is to get at least 150 minutes per week of moderate-intensity physical activity. One way to do this is to try to fit in at least 20 to 25 minutes of activity every day.  https://t.co/VMhUpnDkY4
